1. NETWORK FUNDAMENTALS LABS (4 Labs)
Lab 1.1: OSI Model & Network Devices (6-8 hours)

Understand all 7 OSI layers
Configure basic switches/routers
Test connectivity across layers
Document topology

Lab 1.2: Ethernet & MAC Addressing (5-7 hours)

Master MAC address format
MAC table analysis
Port security configuration
Wireshark packet capture

Lab 1.3: VLAN Configuration (6-8 hours)

Create VLANs 10, 20, 30
Configure trunk ports
Inter-VLAN traffic isolation
SVI configuration

Lab 1.4: Spanning Tree Protocol (7-9 hours)

Redundant loop topology
Root bridge election
Port states and transitions
BPDU monitoring


2. IP CONNECTIVITY LABS (6 Labs)
Lab 2.1: IPv4 Subnetting (8-10 hours)
Lab 2.2: Static Routing (6-8 hours)
Lab 2.3: RIPv2 Configuration (6-8 hours)
Lab 2.4: OSPF (Single & Multi-Area) (10-12 hours)
Lab 2.5: EIGRP Configuration (8-10 hours)
Lab 2.6: BGP Configuration (10-12 hours)

3. IP SERVICES LABS (5 Labs)
Lab 3.1: DHCP | Lab 3.2: DNS | Lab 3.3: NAT & PAT | Lab 3.4: HSRP/VRRP | Lab 3.5: ACLs
(5-9 hours each)

4. SECURITY LABS (4 Labs)
Lab 4.1: AAA | Lab 4.2: IPsec VPN | Lab 4.3: SSL/TLS | Lab 4.4: Zone-Based Firewall
(7-12 hours each)

5. AUTOMATION LABS (4 Labs)
Lab 5.1: Python & Paramiko (12-15 hours)
Lab 5.2: NETCONF & YANG (12-15 hours)
Lab 5.3: REST APIs (IOS-XE) (10-12 hours)
Lab 5.4: Ansible (12-15 hours)

6. COMPREHENSIVE INTEGRATION LABS (4 Labs)
Lab 6.1: Enterprise Multi-Site (18-22 hours)

3-site topology (HQ + 2 branches)
Hierarchical design
OSPF + HSRP + IPsec
Full security implementation

Lab 6.2: Data Center Network (18-22 hours)

Spine-leaf architecture
eBGP + ECMP
VRF + QoS
High availability

Lab 6.3: Security Hardening (18-22 hours)

AAA/TACACS+
Comprehensive logging
Device hardening
Compliance framework

Lab 6.4: Network Automation (22-26 hours)

Python library development
Ansible playbooks
NETCONF/YANG
CI/CD pipeline


STUDY PLAN: 16-20 WEEKS

Phase 1 (Weeks 1-2): Fundamentals - 20-30 hours
Phase 2 (Weeks 3-6): Routing - 40-50 hours
Phase 3 (Weeks 7-8): Services - 25-35 hours
Phase 4 (Weeks 9-10): Security - 30-40 hours
Phase 5 (Weeks 11-12): Automation - 35-45 hours
Phase 6 (Weeks 13-16): Integration & Review - 60-80 hours

TOTAL: 210-280 hours